column5: 4 times today when I tried to visit this site I got the message that it was unavailable. Same message we were receiving awhile back when this site was down.  I've also noticed it sometimes takes awhile for the site to open for me while others are basically instantly.  Just me or are others having issues too ??
No ice, everybody is here instead of fishing
I've had no problems here, Lew.
Thanks Roy, interesting that this is the only site I'm having issues with.
No troubles today, but I got the not available message the other day.
I've had it the odd day where it takes a few extra seconds to light up.
Arts a sleep with his hand on the big red button again. LOL
Been happening to me for a month or so
It's Di, she is putting a limit on your OFC viewing.
Lew when you and I are up between 3 and 4am,this morning,no way was it coming up,have no reason why,sure those in charge may have a idea?.Really throws your morning off lol.
It's Di, she is putting a limit on your OFC viewing.  She hasn't got time for that kind of foolishness John, I keep her too busy doing womens work in the kitchen and laundry room.

Lew when you and I are up between 3 and 4am,this morning,no way was it coming up,have no reason why,sure those in charge may have a idea?.Really throws your morning off lol.  Your bang on davey, I tried to log on at 3:15 this morning and it just said OFC wasn't available.

I find the site is slow to load.  It seems the advertising has to load first before I am able to scroll.  Not a big issue just thought I should mention it.
I had a problem with the site earlier today also, but the next time I tried, about 5 minutes later, all was good.
I do get a "run time script error" from time to time here
I had another insomnia thing last night and I was off and on all night, no problems here.
Unlike you Lew, computers have to sleep from time to time.
Unlike you Lew, computers have to sleep from time to time.  I actually slept for 4 hours the other night MB
